"To mount Windows filesystems using SMB, you will also need smbfs. Enter the "
"command:"
msgstr "要用SMB掛載Windows文件系統，您還需要smbfs。輸入命令："

#: ../generic/server/C/windows-networking.xml:78(command) ../generic/serverguide/C/windows-networking.xml:78(command)
